i.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779570/extras/4aab780d4eb28ba3433481951831abeb.webm?t=1757279202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779570/extras/4aab780d4eb28ba3433481951831abeb.mp4?t=1757279202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
